gen. and sp. nov. 7. Pygofer and segment X, lateral view; 8. Pygofer and segment X, dorsal view; 9. Style, dorsal view; 10. Connective, dorsal view; 11. Female sternite VII, ventral view; 12. Aedeagus, lateral view; 13. Apex of aedeagus, dorsal view; 14. Subgenital plates and valve, ventral view.
</paragraph>
