<taxonomicName box="[348,457,1897,1919]" class="Insecta" family="Cicadellidae" genus="Duocrassana" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hemiptera" pageId="6" pageNumber="585" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="longula">
<emphasis box="[348,457,1897,1919]" italics="true" pageId="6" pageNumber="585">
D. 
<taxonomicName box="[380,457,1897,1919]" pageId="6" pageNumber="585" rank="species" species="longula">longula</taxonomicName>
</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
gen. and sp. nov., female genitalia. 19. First valve, lateral view; 20. Detail of sculpture of first valvula; 21. Second valve, lateral view; 22. Teeth from dorsal margin of second valve; 23. Morphology of tooth; 24. Pygofer, lateral view.
